<div style="position: relative; background: #0f172a; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; font-family: monospace; margin: 20px 0;">
  <button onclick="copyLicense()" 
          style="position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px; 
                 background: #3b82f6; color: white; border: none; 
                 padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; 
                 font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
    📋 Copy License
  </button>

  <pre style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">
<strong>KS Panel License – 2026</strong>

We are excited to share KS Panel with the world!

